Package atos.mae.auto.utils.Exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ActionUndefined
    Exception trigger when action is undefined in excel file.
    DriverNotExistException
    Exception trigger when browser needed is not available.
    NoDriverDefineException
    Exception trigger when an action is call before a webDriver was define.
    PlatformNotFound
    Exception trigger when platform was not found in environment execution json file.
    RangeNameNotFoundException
    Exception trigger when step name not found.
    StepException
    Exception trigger when step have error while loading.
    StepNameNotFound
    Exception trigger when step name not found.
    StepNameUndefined
    Exception trigger when step's name in excel file is undefined.
    StepReturnUndefined
    Exception trigger when a stepReturn is missing.
    TestNameUndefined
    Exception trigger when test's name in TestSet excel file is undefined.
    TypeNotFoundException
    Exception trigger when identifier's type was not found in IdentifierType enum.
    TypeUndefined
    Exception trigger when identifier's type is undefined in ObjectRepository.
    UrlRemoteDriverUndefined
    Exception trigger when remote webDriver url in excel file is undefined.
    WebObjectNotFoundInObjectRepository
    Exception trigger when action is undefined in excel file.
    WrongModuleParameterCount
    Exception trigger when the called module has wrong number of parameter.
